<section class="oe_container">
   <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
        <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive;"><b>Material Purchase Requisition and Cost Sheet Integration</h2>
        <p class="oe_mt32" style="color:olive;">
           This app allow to integration between job cost sheet and material purchase requisition.
        </p>
        <p style="color:CRIMSON;"><b>
            Main Features:
        </p>
        <p style="color:olive;">
            - Allow you to create Job Cost Sheet for Projects/Job Order and plan your Material/Labour/Overheads.<br>
            - Allow you to create Material Purchase Requisition and Allow you to link Job Cost Sheet and Job Cost Line with Material Requisition Line.<br>
            - Using this app you will have complete idea about your planned Material/Labour/Overheads and Actual requested on Material Requisition request.<br>
            - For more details: See <b>Video</b> in live preview<br>
            - For more details about Material Requisition and Job Cost Sheet - Please refer dependant apps link.
        </p>

        <p style="color:CRIMSON;"><b>
            Highlighted Flow:</p>
        <p style="color:green;">
            Create Job Cost Sheets under Project -> Plan your Materials, Labour and Overhead for each Project/Job -> View of Planned and Actual Amount/Qty by each Cost Sheet Lines (Material, Labour and Overheads) -> Allow your Material Purchase Requisition to select Job Cost Center (cost sheet) and Job cost line (cost sheet line) to encode for expenses and labour works..
        </p>
   </div>
</section>

